Text: Takster you are my HERO!! I've been waiting for some VB3.5 skins for ages!!! Thank you!

Perhaps it would be more correct to say that you discovered it a month ago?

vBulletin 3.5.0 was released on September 28th, 2005. That's Gold version. The 3.5RC versions were around even before that. It's been around for 6 months.
